          designs built for the streets!
        </p>
        <div class="mtb-specifications">
          <ul class="mtb-specifications-list">
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Lightweight Frame</li>
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> High Gear Range</li>
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Drop Handlebars</li>
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Aerodynamic Design</li>
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Rigid Fork</li>
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Internal Cable Routing</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="explore-more-btn">Explore More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Road Bikes Section -->
  <section class="hybrid-bikes-section">
    <div class="hybrid-bikes-background">
      <div class="gradient-overlay"></div>
      <div class="content">
        <h4 class="discover-heading">Discover the collection</h4>
        <h2 class="mountain-bikes-heading">Hybrid Bikes</h2>
        <p class="description">Discover the perfect blend of comfort and versatility with our hybrid bikes, designed for
          both city streets and light trails. Enjoy smooth rides with ergonomic features and all-terrain capabilities,
          making every journey effortless and enjoyable!
        </p>
        <div class="mtb-specifications">
          <ul class="mtb-specifications-list">
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Versatile Frame Design</li>
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Comfortable Riding Position</li>
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Front Suspension</li>
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Multi-Terrain Tires</li>
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Comfortable Saddle</li>
            <li class="bullet"><i class="fas fa-bullseye"></i> Wide Gear Range</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <a href="#" class="explore-more-btn">Explore More</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

